00:00:00,010 --> 00:00:33,930
Watch on kissasia.li

1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,680
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 36=

3
00:00:49,583 --> 00:00:51,666
Where do you think you are going,
Leng Xin?

4
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:53,291
So you were hiding in Liuhe Temple.

5
00:00:53,875 --> 00:00:55,750
My master will be angry
if I act on my own.

6
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:56,625
But if I kill you,

7
00:00:56,958 --> 00:00:57,916
he will forgive me.

8
00:01:01,708 --> 00:01:02,791
Leng Xin, King of Killers.

9
00:01:03,416 --> 00:01:05,083
You slaughter innocents
and treat lives as dirt.

10
00:01:05,375 --> 00:01:06,541
A thousand deaths are on your hands.

11
00:01:06,875 --> 00:01:08,458
The Bounty List offers
ten thousand gold for you.

12
00:01:08,666 --> 00:01:09,458
Dead or alive.

13
00:01:30,833 --> 00:01:32,958
Xintian, can you hit

14
00:01:32,958 --> 00:01:33,583
my new mini thunderfire bomb?

15
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,166
I will use fake thunderfire bombs
to split them up.

16
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:37,833
Find your chance and shoot Leng Xin.

17
00:02:42,041 --> 00:02:42,541
Young Master Chang!

18
00:02:56,083 --> 00:02:56,541
Hua!

19
00:03:04,625 --> 00:03:05,416
Surround the gate!

20
00:03:05,541 --> 00:03:05,958
Yes!

21
00:03:40,916 --> 00:03:41,416
Leng Xin.

22
00:03:41,791 --> 00:03:43,750
Do you serve Prince Fu
or the Crown Prince?

23
00:03:44,416 --> 00:03:45,833
I won't tell you.

24
00:03:47,833 --> 00:03:49,083
You think you won?

25
00:03:50,041 --> 00:03:52,958
Who said Leng Xin was only one person?

26
00:03:57,125 --> 00:03:57,916
What do you mean?

27
00:03:58,375 --> 00:03:59,541
Are you really Leng Xin or not?

28
00:04:01,041 --> 00:04:01,958
You want to know?

29
00:04:02,916 --> 00:04:04,666
Then I will never give you the answer.

30
00:04:15,791 --> 00:04:17,333
Are you the real Leng Xin or not?

31
00:04:30,250 --> 00:04:30,958
Guokai!

32
00:06:08,208 --> 00:06:11,208
(Righteousness of Heaven and Earth)

33
00:06:32,470 --> 00:06:37,270
(Jinyiwei Northern Bureau)

34
00:06:39,416 --> 00:06:40,333
You are saying

35
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,208
she was not Leng Xin?

36
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:45,041
Then who?

37
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:46,916
My lord.

38
00:06:47,708 --> 00:06:48,750
Look at Taozi's age.

39
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:52,291
Could she be the Leng Xin
who killed my father and the witness?

40
00:06:52,958 --> 00:06:54,000
What do you mean?

41
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:56,500
I mean,

42
00:06:56,958 --> 00:06:58,500
Leng Xin may not be one person.

43
00:07:03,208 --> 00:07:04,333
What else could she be? A ghost?

44
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:06,500
Leng Xin may be a group of people.

45
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:07,916
Or an organization.

46
00:07:10,625 --> 00:07:11,458
Do you have proof?

47
00:07:12,458 --> 00:07:13,333
No.

48
00:07:24,083 --> 00:07:25,625
I thought you might fight
with Zhang again.

49
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:26,833
Not anymore.

50
00:07:27,333 --> 00:07:29,000
I'm no longer that Shen Bingfan,

51
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,375
always angry and quick to lose control.

52
00:07:31,125 --> 00:07:32,583
I advised the Commander

53
00:07:32,833 --> 00:07:33,875
to handle this quietly.

54
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:36,458
Bingfan.

55
00:07:37,166 --> 00:07:37,833
You have grown up.

56
00:07:41,125 --> 00:07:42,125
As for Leng Xin,

57
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:43,750
I will keep investigating.

58
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:44,625
But

59
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:46,458
I won't rush anymore.

60
00:07:51,875 --> 00:07:53,125
(Honest and Upright)

61
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:54,000
(Honest and Upright)
Good.

62
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,666
(Honest and Upright)
This Ghost Festival,

63
00:07:57,291 --> 00:08:00,041
our Northern Bureau laid
a brilliant Empty Fort trap

64
00:08:00,708 --> 00:08:01,708
and eliminated

65
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:05,333
(Honest and Upright)
Leng Xin, the Bounty List's top killer.

66
00:08:06,291 --> 00:08:07,083
Excellent.

67
00:08:07,875 --> 00:08:08,833
In this operation,

68
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,416
our female Jinyiwei acted swiftly

69
00:08:11,083 --> 00:08:11,916
and planned well.

70
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:12,833
I already

71
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:13,791
reported this

72
00:08:14,416 --> 00:08:15,416
to His Majesty.

73
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,625
His Majesty heard the news

74
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:17,875
and was greatly pleased.

75
00:08:18,291 --> 00:08:18,500
He has

76
00:08:19,125 --> 00:08:19,958
formally promoted

77
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:23,083
Shen Bingfan to Qianhu.

78
00:08:25,208 --> 00:08:26,000
Hua Mange

79
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:27,583
and Cheng Xintian

80
00:08:28,291 --> 00:08:30,458
are formally promoted to Baihu.

81
00:08:32,833 --> 00:08:33,541
Xu Duoyu

82
00:08:33,958 --> 00:08:34,625
is promoted to

83
00:08:35,041 --> 00:08:36,125
Chief Squad Leader.

84
00:08:40,708 --> 00:08:41,750
We thank His Majesty
for his boundless grace.

85
00:08:41,916 --> 00:08:43,958
Long live His Majesty!

86
00:08:46,958 --> 00:08:47,333
Good.

87
00:09:26,333 --> 00:09:28,458
The spring wind dares
to brush the willows.

88
00:09:29,166 --> 00:09:30,375
The night rain comes unseen

89
00:09:31,041 --> 00:09:32,000
to nourish the flowers.

90
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,541
Take him!

91
00:09:35,916 --> 00:09:37,416
Go!

92
00:09:45,416 --> 00:09:46,083
Shen Bingfan.

93
00:09:48,916 --> 00:09:49,791
Until we meet again
in the martial world.

94
00:10:11,375 --> 00:10:12,416
Feng Fuliu really is alive.

95
00:10:15,833 --> 00:10:16,333
Is he?

96
00:10:18,125 --> 00:10:19,291
You don't seem surprised.

97
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:21,875
Now you have something to do.

98
00:10:22,916 --> 00:10:23,375
Yes.

99
00:10:24,375 --> 00:10:25,333
As long as he is alive,

100
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,708
I won't stop chasing him.

101
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:30,041
Then, when will you

102
00:10:30,416 --> 00:10:31,750
come home with me to meet my parents?

103
00:10:34,291 --> 00:10:34,791
Beiming.

104
00:10:40,208 --> 00:10:40,958
Tomorrow. Same place.

105
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:43,458
I will give you an answer.

106
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,041
(Hua.)

107
00:11:40,166 --> 00:11:40,791
(Forgive me.)

108
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:44,208
(The Leng Xin who killed my parents
is still out there.)

109
00:11:45,458 --> 00:11:46,500
(Until that person is caught,)

110
00:11:47,625 --> 00:11:48,833
(I cannot confess my feelings to you.)

111
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,100
(Spirit of My Beloved Fa Yuanrong)

112
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:41,041
Yuanrong.

113
00:12:42,125 --> 00:12:44,083
We finally avenged you.

114
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:53,833
(Spirit Tablet of My Sworn Brother,
Lord Shen Lian, Qianhu)

115
00:12:53,833 --> 00:12:54,541
(Spirit Tablet of My Sworn Brother)
Shen.

116
00:12:55,458 --> 00:12:56,541
Our secret

117
00:12:58,583 --> 00:13:00,208
is safe for now.

118
00:13:43,833 --> 00:13:44,208
Father.

119
00:13:45,125 --> 00:13:45,458
Mother.

120
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,000
(Grave of My Late Parents)
Leng Xin has been brought to justice.

121
00:13:50,083 --> 00:13:50,916
But I know

122
00:13:51,666 --> 00:13:53,291
she was not the Leng Xin who killed you.

123
00:13:54,375 --> 00:13:55,583
So I won't give up.

124
00:13:57,541 --> 00:13:58,541
I will keep investigating.

125
00:13:59,958 --> 00:14:01,541
I will catch every Leng Xin

126
00:14:03,041 --> 00:14:04,666
and bring them all to justice.

127
00:14:09,625 --> 00:14:10,000
Father.

128
00:14:11,875 --> 00:14:12,958
You taught me

129
00:14:13,416 --> 00:14:14,416
what justice is,

130
00:14:15,958 --> 00:14:16,916
what courage is,

131
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:19,166
and what fairness means.

132
00:14:21,791 --> 00:14:22,958
So no matter who you were

133
00:14:24,291 --> 00:14:25,291
or what your true allegiance was,

134
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,375
I will always

135
00:14:32,041 --> 00:14:33,833
follow what I know is right.

136
00:14:36,041 --> 00:14:36,750
With a righteous heart,

137
00:14:38,458 --> 00:14:39,375
one is invincible.

138
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:48,680
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

139
00:14:53,375 --> 00:14:53,833
I'm here.

140
00:14:56,291 --> 00:14:56,791
Today,

141
00:14:57,220 --> 00:15:00,180
♪I whisper in my heart♪

142
00:15:00,208 --> 00:15:01,083
I will give you my answer.

143
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:08,520
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

144
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:12,140
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

145
00:15:12,140 --> 00:15:15,430
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

146
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:20,100
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

147
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:23,180
♪Round and round♪

148
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:27,930
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

149
00:15:27,930 --> 00:15:32,810
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

150
00:15:34,140 --> 00:15:41,020
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

151
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:44,470
♪This longing I cannot say♪

152
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:47,437
♪I wish you♪

153
00:15:47,437 --> 00:15:52,220
♪could hear♪

154
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:57,850
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

155
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:05,600
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

156
00:16:05,850 --> 00:16:09,060
♪This longing I cannot say♪

157
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:11,521
♪Tucked away♪

158
00:16:11,979 --> 00:16:16,600
♪inside my heart♪

159
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:22,520
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

160
00:16:23,390 --> 00:16:30,350
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

161
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:33,770
♪This longing I cannot say♪

162
00:16:33,770 --> 00:16:39,310
♪I wish you could hear♪

163
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:46,020
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

164
00:16:47,930 --> 00:16:54,930
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

165
00:16:54,930 --> 00:16:58,470
♪This longing I cannot say♪

166
00:16:58,470 --> 00:17:03,470
♪Tucked away inside my heart♪

167
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:29,350
(Leng Xin)

168
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:36,430
(Leng Xin)

169
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:43,187
(Leng Xin)

170
00:18:03,416 --> 00:18:05,500
Master, this is Leng Xin's sword.

171
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:48,190
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

172
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:51,940
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

173
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:55,190
♪My heart drifted lost♪

174
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:58,600
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

175
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:02,900
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

176
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:06,650
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

177
00:19:07,230 --> 00:19:09,440
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

178
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:13,480
♪I've softly let it go♪

179
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:17,350
♪The vow you made was true♪

180
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:21,100
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

181
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:23,310
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

182
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:27,850
♪And forget at world's end♪

183
00:19:28,150 --> 00:19:29,650
♪Embracing memory♪

184
00:19:29,650 --> 00:19:32,020
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

185
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:35,900
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

186
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:38,230
♪I wish to let it pass♪

187
00:19:38,230 --> 00:19:43,230
♪And run toward this vast life♪

